0ae759f4bd3f07e4360173306","tid":734457,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"請問幾時報堂嫁？你又讀左幾多個月呢？<br />\n用信用卡每個月過數定係點？<br />\n比較少聽到呢間野有問題... 但繼續留意下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:04:38.000Z","msg":"讀咗幾個月啦 根本抽唔到時間上 佢地本身堂又少<br />\n用信用卡每月過數呀屌<br />\n同銀行講佢地話間野可以拎份合約繼續收錢 未必斷到尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"CUT卡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:00:32.000Z","msg":"細公司就或者得，有返咁上下規模既同你玩法律途徑告鳩你毁約慢慢玩都得。"},{"pid":"b9a4541cf1ac07f22d12a78d736f06bedaa6b1c6","tid":734457,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"樓主，銷委會得個名，一佢只係負責聯絡調停，二佢無法定權力去告間公司，三來佢無法定權力去做調查，公司一唔會作佢就企係到。<br />\n不過你個情況照睇就實走唔甩，就算上到庭都會比人問到口啞啞，唔通個個報左課程之類一個唔該就來緊唔得閒就可以取消合約。你就你有重病上唔到都可以講嘈下，而家係你自己選擇其他野而放棄佢。"},{"pid":"1fb4cfe5c9f4e33b81c66c082af85e132ad4a2ee","tid":734457,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1461b1aaf5c47e6b166f72e2a97052ae4714f1","tid":734457,"uid":150568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有啲長同sorly for 1999<br />\n<br />\n我報咗Wall Street English 18個月的課程。<br />\n簽約期間，我當時冇睇清楚條款內容，而分校職員都冇詳細說明條約內容，直接叫我簽名。期後我發現終止課程校方只接受三個原因：一.危疾 二.死亡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三.永久離港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/234020_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F234020_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=11a78c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後因為我嚟緊會開始讀一個三年既part-time degree，將唔會有空閒上堂，所以就書面申請咗要退學。<br />\n<br />\n兩個禮拜之後終於收到回覆，拒絕咗退學申請，原因係唔符合嗰三個條件。佢地提出三個替代方案：一.報讀其他課程（但我根本沒有時間上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）二.轉移合約俾其他人 （CLS個19合約仲要轉俾人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）三.凍結課程（三年之後再上堂，但期間繼續要扣錢on99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">消費者及不公平合約條款：法律保障不足及相關改革建議<br />\n</span></strong><a href=\"http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-lawyer.org%2Ftc%2Fcontent%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AC%25BE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=CJMkycaNPSOu6GMVJ4Fa24S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=83b09fff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk-lawyer.org/tc/content/%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B9%B3%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n之前睇到有一條《不合情理合約條例》(第458章) ，想知道下一步可以點做。我將會約消委會諮詢一下。<br />\n<br />\nPS: 知道自己簽約on9 插輕力啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"無架喇<br />\n你只怪自己無做捉功課同心急<br />\n<br />\n受害者之1"},{"pid":"26310c330caf8655c0e94ce21bd9a31b1d25a07d","tid":734457,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b5fcaa7c039eec209f948419c1bf71acc457faa","tid":734457,"uid":186647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1461b1aaf5c47e6b166f72e2a97052ae4714f1","tid":734457,"uid":150568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15: